    "ftbquests.chapter.vampires_cookbook.quest8132643229579864808.description1":"你仍然可以吃正常的食物来获得额外的生命值！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.vampires_cookbook.quest8132643229579864808.title":"小窍门！",
